#circuitbreakersg day 43

Western day~

What a spread 😱😍 Oven baked honey garlic salmon. Salmon from @9sseafood 
Oven baked black pepper chicken with potatoes. Black pepper chicken from @fairpricesg 
Garlic breadstick. Ciabatta bread from @friendsofgardenia 
Cheesy baked mushroom using @emborgasia cheese
Tomato fusilli using Naturel pasta
Tempura kani stick

#stayhome #jxeatshome
@kerinsaur hehe glad that u like my mum’s pasta 😍
@sle.travelandeats 😅😅 it’s simple to prep. jus sprinkle salt n pepper, add garlic butter spread and honey. bake in oven! thank you😍
That is such an amazing spread. Please come to mine and cook for us! Ha!
Love this! Such a nice spread
